REM windows_open_browser.duck
REM Opens the default browser to a target URL via the Run dialog.
REM Edit the STRING line to change the destination URL.
REM Works on Windows 10 and 11 with any default browser.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE ON
HUMAN_SPEED NORMAL

REM Open Run dialog
GUI r
DELAY 600

REM Paste URL — Run dialog forwards it to the default browser
STRING https://example.com
ENTER
